ation was collected\n\nFor failed or partial snapshots, store a coarse `error_kind` if useful for\ndebugging or telemetry, such as `context_unavailable`, `workspace_unavailable`,\nor `diff_unavailable`. Do not store raw error strings in the shared turn\nmetadata by default.\n\nConcrete turn detail example:\n","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-20T01:48:55.429Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}}